    ('wispr-flow', 'How do you actually use Wispr Flow during work?', array['Speak naturally and it transcribes plus auto-formats clean text into whatever app you''re in','Drag video files in to get a script','Type prompts to render images','Connect it to ad accounts to push budgets'], 0),
    ('manus', 'What kind of task is Manus designed to take off your plate?', array['Writing a single tweet','Running multi-step agentic workflows that browse, fill forms and produce artefacts','Editing raw camera RAW files','Hosting your company wiki'], 1),
    ('cursor', 'What is Cursor, in one sentence?', array['A no-code site builder','An AI-native fork of VS Code where you can prompt edits across multiple files','A Figma plugin that exports React','A serverless database'], 1),
    ('lovable', 'Who is Lovable mainly built for?', array['Senior backend engineers writing distributed systems','Hardware engineers designing chips','Non-engineers (PMs, marketers, founders) shipping working web apps from a prompt','Game studios making AAA titles'], 2),
