    ('base44', 'Where does Base44 sit in the stack?', array['It''s a video editor','It''s a no-code AI app builder for internal tools, where you describe a tool and get a working app with auth and a database','It''s a GPU-rental marketplace','It''s an SEO crawler'], 1),
    ('emergent', 'Which problem does Emergent target?', array['Pure prompt-to-app generation aimed at non-technical operators who want full-stack apps without touching code','Translating subtitles for streaming platforms','Rendering 3D product shots','Mixing music masters'], 0),
    ('heygen', 'What does HeyGen let a marketing team produce quickly?', array['Spreadsheet macros','AI-avatar videos and translated lip-synced versions of existing footage at scale','Lo-fi music tracks','Cold-email sequences'], 1),
