    ('artlist', 'What is Artlist primarily a source of?', array['Royalty-free music, SFX, footage and AI tools licensed for commercial use','Influencer outreach contacts','Print-on-demand fulfilment','Stock options for startups'], 0),
    ('canva', 'Why is Canva listed as an AI tool, not just a design tool?', array['It only does AI image generation now','Magic Studio adds AI generation, resizing, on-brand templates and bulk-create across formats inside one workspace','It''s a code IDE','It hosts your domains'], 1),
    ('figma', 'Which Figma capability best matches an AI workflow?', array['Generating brand-aware UI mockups, variants and copy via Figma AI inside the design file','Running paid social','Sending invoices','Encoding video for streaming'], 0),
    ('designs-ai', 'What does Designs.ai try to be?', array['A SQL editor','An all-in-one creative suite — logos, video, voice, copy, mockups — generated from a prompt','A monitoring tool for servers','An online whiteboard for engineering'], 1),
